      "width": 800,
      "height": 350,
      "text": "Per planned ad unit: build ads_context items\nFor each {persona, format} in plan:\n1) Load persona from playbook:\n   parse_persona_library(AD_CREATIVE_SYSTEM_PLAYBOOK.md)\n   build_persona_payload(persona_no)\n\n2) Extract format rules:\n   scripts/extract_format_rules.py --format <fmt> --json\n\n3) Build copy_requirements:\n   build_copy_requirements(persona_no, fmt, seq_index)\n   ✅ lanes removed:\n   - copies only structural constraints\n   - LLM chooses headline/support freely from master doc\n\n4) Apply hypothesis override:\n   If hypothesis active, inject concept variations:\n   - concept.audience_stage / lead_angle / message_structure\n   - OR hook_structure_override / proof_style_override / cta_voice_override\n\n5) Append to ads_context:\n   {persona, format_rules, format, copy_requirements, hypothesis}\n\nRegistry banlist:\n- scripts/registry_banlist.py produces banlist buckets",
