      "text": "Generate copy (LLM step)\nFull context saved:\n- context/run_context.json includes:\n  - product_context (from extractor)\n  - ads[] with persona/format_rules/copy_requirements/hypothesis\n  - banlist\n\nCall OpenCode:\n- call_opencode_compatible(cfg, full_context, run_dir)\n- system prompt instructs strict JSON schema\n- uses build_generation_payload_for_llm(single_context)\n\nHypothesis testing mechanics:\n- Candidate generation must match requested hypothesis fields\n- validate with hypothesis_mismatch():\n  - hook_structure: checks headline opening via classify_hook_structure()\n  - concept_angle/structure checks\n  - proof_style / cta_voice checks via classifiers\n- If mismatch → retry prompt with REVISION_REQUIRED\n\nFallback if OpenCode fails:\n- llm_mode = fallback_template\n- uses build_template_copy(full_context, run_id)\n\nNormalization + scrubbing:\n- normalize_generated_copy()\n- strip_internal_markers_from_payload()\n- enforce_unique_ctas() via AD_GENERATION_REGISTRY.JSON\n- scrub_on_image_copy() (removes context_line proof notes)\n\nFinal output stored:\n- context/copy_batch.json",
